c: 6
v: 157
t: "or, so that you do not say, \"If a Book had been sent down to us, we would have followed its guidance better than they did.\" Clear evidence, guidance and mercy has come to you from your Lord. Who could be more unjust than someone who rejects God's messages and turns away in contempt? We will recompense those who turn away from Our verses with the worst of punishment for their having turned away"